    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just about being \"not perfect\" though. every time i screw up, i see it in their faces. they're growing up in this constant cloud of stress because of me. i feel like a poison in their lives. honestly, i feel like the only way they could actually have a chance at being happy is if i wasn't constantly dragging them down.",
